The paper discusses the behavior of massive MIMO systems in large-scale and extra-large scale regimes, which are related to information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), control systems (cs.SY), multimedia (cs.MM), and computer communication (cs.COM). The paper also mentions MIMO design aspects, which further supports the likelihood of these categories.
